Subscriber Services

To subscribe, update your address, renew subscription, pass the Newsletter along to a friend 
or have them subscribe free go to: http://www.sensorsportal.com/HTML/subscribe.htm

Do you have comments about this newsletter? Send them to Sensors Web Portal at 
mailto:info@sensorsportal.com

To unsubscribe from the Newsletter, reply to this e-mail message, enter "Remove" in Subject 
line and the following text in the body of the message: remove <your email address> and mention 
all the e-mail addresses to be removed with any e-mail addresses, which might be diverting the 
e-mails to you. Be sure, that you have received this Newsletter to <your email address>.

Alternatively, you can visit http://www.sensorsportal.com/HTML/Nospam.htm and click 
<Unsubscribe> (enable Java applet option required).

If you cannot unsubscribe, the most common reason is that you receive our newsletter at one 
email address and are trying to unsubscribe from another (33 % persons who ask about 
unsubscribtion do it). You can still remove yourself from our list send us e-mail for personal 
assistance.

